        "text_7ANXgn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The<a href=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/dipstick-pro%E2%84%A2\" title=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/dipstick-pro%E2%84%A2\"> DipStick Pro™ </a>is a reliable and easy-to-use core sampler engineered to accurately determine the levels of grease, solids, and sludge in grease traps, interceptors, septic systems, clarifiers, and sludge basins. Trusted by pretreatment experts nationwide, the <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> is the tool of choice when precise, consistent, and legally defensible core samples are needed for evaluating FOG accumulation in containment units. Known for its rugged build, simplicity, and superior accuracy, it surpasses tools like the Sludge Judge in performance.</p><p></p><p>Beyond grease systems, the DipStick Pro™ is highly adaptable and provides dependable measurements of liquid levels in various storage tanks, including those holding oil, fuel, and other liquid substances.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
