        "text_Mqytwd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <a href=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/dipstick-pro%E2%84%A2\" title=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/dipstick-pro%E2%84%A2\"><strong>DipStick Pro™</strong></a> is a simple-to-use core sampling tool designed to precisely measure levels of grease, solids, or sludge in grease traps, interceptors, septic systems, clarifiers, and sludge basins.</p><p>Widely trusted by pretreatment professionals across the U.S., the <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> is the go-to tool when accurate, consistent, and defensible core samples of FOG levels are needed in traps, interceptors, lift stations, and sludge pits.</p><p>Crafted from corrosion-resistant, precision-machined aluminum and durable, impact-resistant resin, the <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> stands alone as the only core sampler featuring “ball valve” technology to ensure a true and undisturbed core sample.</p><p>A user-friendly T-handle and arm lever system controls the ball valve, allowing consistent operation and ensuring reliable, repeatable samples every time.</p><p>The <strong>DipStick Pro™</strong> comes in a standard 10-foot length (two sections—6’ and 4’) connected by a quick-coupling system for fast assembly. Extensions can be ordered to suit deeper systems. Unlike other samplers that include components disrupting the sample, the DipStick Pro™ provides clean, accurate measurements without distortion.</p><p>As the most rugged and reliable FOG sampler available, the DipStick Pro™ delivers a precise sample every single time.</p><p><strong>Simple Operation:</strong></p><ul><li>Insert DipStick Pro™ into the interceptor or trap</li><li>Pull the actuator handle to seal the ball valve and collect the sample</li><li>Remove the tool and wipe clean to inspect the contents</li><li>Log the measured grease, water, and solids</li></ul><p>Custom lengths can be tailored to meet your sampling needs. Contact us by phone or email for details.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
